	(text "ephemerkey — Accelerometer (U5 LIS3DHTR, LGA-16). PLACED, not wired. See DESIGN.md Sensors / Security.\nSUPPLY: VDD(14)+VDD_IO(1)->+3V3, C23/C24 100nF each. GND(5,12)->GND. RES(10)->GND. ADC1-3(13,15,16)=NC. CS(8)->+3V3 (force I2C).\nI2C1: SCL(4)->PB6, SDA(6)->PB7; R9/R10 4.7k pull-ups to +3V3. SDO/SA0(7) strap sets addr (0x18 low / 0x19 high).\nINT: INT1(11)->PA2 (wake-on-motion), INT2(9)->PA3 (tamper/free-fall). Tamper policy may zeroize the TOTP secret (DESIGN.md Security)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.00 95.00 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
		(uuid "247040dc-a967-47e7-b7f3-ae5ffd863a2c")
	)
